<TEXT>
<P>
The rejection of Tower should sound a warning to all. Tower was denied the post 
because of alcohol abuse. It is time for everyone to remember that alcohol is a 
drug and drug abuse will get you. Just because alcohol has been maintained as a 
legal drug by a well-entrenched industry does not mean that it is not a 
dangerous drug. MADD (Mothers Against Drunk Driving) is a household word 
because alcohol abuse is fatally dangerous. 
</P>
