We all look at derelicts sleeping in the streets, clutching their bottles of 
booze, and say, "That could never happen to me." Look at Tower and ask 
yourself, "Could that happen to me?" If your answer is, "Nah, I just drink to 
have fun," then you, too, have a drug problem. 
