FREE TRADE PAC; SENATE (U.S); LEGISLATORS; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT 
OFFICIALS; AUTOMOBILE INDUSTRY -- JAPAN; FOREIGN OWNED CORPORATIONS 
</P>
