taking amnesty test with co-workers at the Irvine Marriott. DON TORMEY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Dinora Benavides of Santa Ana gets congratulatory hug and 
kiss from Harold Ezell, INS Western regional commissioner. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
