<TEXT>
<P>
Catcher Lisa Sciarrino hit a double in the top of the eighth inning to give 
Western High School a 1-0 victory over Woodbridge in 4-A division pool play of 
the Canyon softball tournament Friday at Canyon High School. 
</P>
