and allowed only four hits. 
</P>
<P>
Qubypo needed help from Dawn Fowler and Sciarrino in the bottom of the eighth. 
Fowler entered the game with no outs and a runner on second. Sciarrino picked 
the runner off and Fowler struck out the last two batters for the save. 
