(3-3, 3-0) won all nine singles sets at Brea-Olinda. 
</P>
<P>
Western 14, Savanna 4 -- Ed Peregrino won his sets, 6-0, 6-2, 6-1, for the 
Pioneers (7-2, 2-1) at Western. 
</P>
<P>
In nonleague tennis: 
</P>
<P>
El Toro 13, Foothill 5 -- Chris Brown swept, 7-6, 6-4, 6-1, as the Chargers 
(8-0) won seven of nine singles sets at El Toro. 
</P>
<P>
Irvine 17, Trabuco Hills 1 -- Cory Beacham swept his singles sets, 6-0, 6-2, 
6-0, for the Vaqueros (4-3) at Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
Mission Viejo 12, Laguna Beach 6 -- Mission Viejo (9-0) swept the doubles 
matches at Laguna Beach. Laguna Beach (4-1) played without its two top players, 
Jon Leach and Graham Gillis, who are playing at the Easter Bowl tournament in 
Florida. 
</P>
<P>
In Garden Grove League volleyball: 
</P>
<P>
