as Garden Grove (2-3, 2-0) swept, 15-5, 15-3, 15-7, at Garden Grove. 
</P>
<P>
Pacifica 3, Los Amigos 0 -- Jason Guthrie had 11 kills and Eric Cadacio had 19 
assists, as Pacifica (2-1, 2-0) swept, 15-2, 15-3, 15-5, at Los Amigos. 
</P>
